import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import Cards from './Cards'
import './index.css'

ReactDOM.render(
  <>
    <Cards
      imgsrc="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80057281"
      category="A Netflix Original Series"
      title="DARK"
      link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80100172"
      button="Watch Dark"
    />

    <Cards
      imgsrc="https://picsum.photos/seed/picsum/200/300"
      category="A Netflix Original Series"
      title="SACRED GAMES"
      link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80115328"
      button="Watch SACRED GAMES"
    />

    <Cards
      imgsrc="https://picsum.photos/200/300?grayscale"
      category="A Netflix Original Series"
      title="STRANGER THINGS"
      link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80057281"
      button="Watch STRANGER THINGS"
    />
  </>
  , document.getElementById('root'));
